@startuml sequence-booking-grooming
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram — Booking Grooming (End-to-End)

actor Pelanggan
actor "Staff / Owner" as Staff
participant "Aplikasi Web" as App
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB

== Ajukan Booking ==

Pelanggan -> App : Buka menu Grooming
App -> API : GET /grooming/kuota?tanggal=...
API -> DB : SELECT kuota_grooming
DB --> API : Kuota tersedia
API --> App : Daftar tanggal & sisa kuota
App --> Pelanggan : Tampilkan kuota per tanggal

Pelanggan -> App : Isi form booking\n(kucing, jenis, tanggal, opsi pengantaran)
alt Antar-jemput & alamat belum lengkap
  App --> Pelanggan : Wajib lengkapi alamat profil
else Antar-jemput & alamat lengkap
  App -> API : POST /grooming/estimasi-pickup
  API -> API : Hitung jarak & biaya\n(gratis ≤3km, charge >3km)
  API --> App : jarak_km, biaya_antar_jemput
  App --> Pelanggan : Tampilkan estimasi biaya
else Antar sendiri
  App --> Pelanggan : biaya antar-jemput = Rp 0
end

Pelanggan -> App : Submit booking
App -> API : POST /booking/grooming
API -> DB : Cek sisa kuota_grooming
API -> DB : INSERT booking_grooming\nstatus = MENUNGGU_KONFIRMASI
API -> DB : UPDATE kuota_grooming.slot_terisi +1
API -> DB : INSERT transaksi (draft)
DB --> API : OK
API --> App : 201 Created
App --> Pelanggan : Booking diajukan

== Konfirmasi & Set Jam (Staff) ==

Staff -> App : Buka daftar booking masuk
App -> API : GET /internal/booking/grooming
API -> DB : SELECT booking_grooming
DB --> API : Daftar booking
API --> App : Data booking
App --> Staff : Tampilkan daftar

alt Staff tolak booking
  Staff -> App : Tolak booking
  App -> API : PATCH /internal/booking/grooming/{id}/tolak
  API -> DB : UPDATE status = DIBATALKAN
  API -> DB : UPDATE kuota slot_terisi -1
  API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi BOOKING_DITOLAK
  DB --> API : OK
  API --> App : OK
  App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi booking ditolak
else Staff konfirmasi
  Staff -> App : Konfirmasi & isi jam grooming
  App -> API : PATCH /internal/booking/grooming/{id}/konfirmasi
  API -> DB : UPDATE jam_grooming, status = MENUNGGU_PEMBAYARAN
  API -> DB : UPDATE transaksi.batas_waktu_bayar
  API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi JAM_GROOMING_DIUPDATE
  DB --> API : OK
  API --> App : OK
  App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi jam & tagihan
end

== Pembayaran & Verifikasi ==

Pelanggan -> App : Transfer & upload bukti transfer
App -> API : POST /transaksi/{id}/bukti-transfer
API -> DB : INSERT bukti_transfer
API -> DB : UPDATE status = MENUNGGU_VERIFIKASI_BUKTI
DB --> API : OK
API --> App : OK
App --> Pelanggan : Menunggu verifikasi staff

Staff -> App : Review bukti transfer
alt Bukti ditolak
  Staff -> App : Tolak bukti + catatan
  App -> API : PATCH /internal/bukti-transfer/{id}/tolak
  API -> DB : UPDATE status_verifikasi = DITOLAK
  API --> App : OK
  App --> Pelanggan : Diminta upload ulang
else Bukti disetujui
  Staff -> App : Setujui bukti
  App -> API : PATCH /internal/bukti-transfer/{id}/setujui
  API -> DB : UPDATE transaksi status = LUNAS
  API -> DB : UPDATE booking status = TERKONFIRMASI
  API -> DB : INSERT invoice
  API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi
  DB --> API : OK
  API --> App : OK
  App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi lunas + unduh invoice
end

== Proses Layanan ==

Staff -> App : Update status → Sedang Proses → Selesai
App -> API : PATCH /internal/booking/grooming/{id}/status
API -> DB : UPDATE status booking
API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi LAYANAN_SELESAI
DB --> API : OK
API --> App : OK
App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi layanan selesai

@enduml
